code: /**  * Returns {@code true} if the given {@link SequenceNumber} is a sentinel.  */ public static boolean isSentinelSequenceNumber(SequenceNumber candidateSequenceNumber) {     for (SentinelSequenceNumber sentinel : values()) {         if (candidateSequenceNumber.equals(sentinel.get())) {             return true.         }     }     return false. }
